---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="OEM/ODM Customization | SaiWei Sport"
  description="OEM/ODM customization for sports goods including logo printing, sublimation teamwear, artwork support and private label packaging."
  activePage="oem-odm"
>
  <main>
    <section class="pagehero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label"><span></span> OEM/ODM Customization</div>
        <h1>Turn sports goods into your own branded product line.</h1>
        <p class="lead">SaiWei Sport supports logo printing, teamwear sublimation, artwork development, private-label packaging and mixed-category custom orders for global B2B buyers.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="lab">
          <div class="big">
            <div class="kicker">Custom Brand Lab</div>
            <h2>High-end customization, not generic sports supply.</h2>
            <p>We help buyers upgrade ordinary products into branded collections: matching colors, professional artwork placement, private-label packaging and consistent product presentation across multiple categories.</p>
            <div class="pills">
              <span class="pill">Logo</span>
              <span class="pill">Artwork</span>
              <span class="pill">Colors</span>
              <span class="pill">Packaging</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tiles">
            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Logo & Artwork</h3>
              <p>Logo printing, heat-transfer graphics, sublimation layouts, club badges and sponsor positions.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Colors & Collections</h3>
              <p>Create football, basketball and training collections with consistent brand colors.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Names & Numbers</h3>
              <p>Teamwear customization for clubs, schools, academies and league orders.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="tile">
              <h3>Retail Packaging</h3>
              <p>Private-label poly bags, hang tags, cartons and Amazon-ready product presentation.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section soft">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
          <div>
            <div class="kicker">Service System</div>
            <h2>OEM/ODM support for every buyer type.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Whether you need a single product or a complete collection, we help structure the project from concept to delivery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid4">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Product Selection</h3>
            <p>Choose football, basketball, teamwear, shin guards or mixed product combinations.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Visual Identity</h3>
            <p>Match product colors, logo placement, patterns and packaging with your brand direction.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Sampling Plan</h3>
            <p>Confirm physical details through sampling before large-scale production.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Bulk Delivery</h3>
            <p>Manage production, inspection, carton packing and international shipment coordination.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="title">
          <div>
            <div class="kicker">Custom Process</div>
            <h2>From product idea to global delivery.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>A clear process gives international buyers confidence and makes complex custom orders easier to confirm.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process">
          <article class="step">
            <div class="stepno">1</div>
            <h3>Select Product Type</h3>
            <p>Choose footballs, uniforms, basketballs, basketball uniforms, shin guards or mixed orders.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="stepno">2</div>
            <h3>Send Brand Details</h3>
            <p>Share logos, colors, size charts, artwork, packaging ideas and target market requirements.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="stepno">3</div>
            <h3>Confirm Mockup</h3>
            <p>Review layout, product specs, materials, quantity, packaging and quotation details.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="stepno">4</div>
            <h3>Sample & Inspect</h3>
            <p>Approve sample direction and confirm production details before bulk manufacturing.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <div class="stepno">5</div>
            <h3>Produce & Ship</h3>
            <p>Mass production, packing, inspection and global delivery coordination for B2B buyers.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
